---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy — ReelClarity"
	description="ReelClarity's privacy policy: your videos are processed entirely on your device and are never uploaded, stored, or transmitted to any server."
	canonicalPath="/privacy"
>
	<section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#2B2013] sm:text-4xl">
			Privacy Policy
		</h1>
		<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-[#8A7D67]">Last updated: 2026</p>

		<div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-[#5C4F3D] leading-relaxed">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#2B2013]">Your files never leave your device</h2>
			<p>
				ReelClarity processes video entirely client-side, in your browser.
				When you choose a file, it is read locally and enhanced using
				JavaScript running on your own device. At no point is the video file
				uploaded, transmitted, or sent to any server we operate. We have no
				way to see, store, or access the videos you process.
			</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#2B2013]">What we don't collect</h2>
			<p>
				We do not require an account, we do not ask for your email, and we do
				not store your files. Nothing about the content of your video (its
				name, size, or pixels) is transmitted anywhere.
			</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#2B2013]">Standard web analytics</h2>
			<p>
				Like most websites, basic, aggregated analytics (such as page views)
				and advertising may be served on this site through third-party
				providers. These providers may use cookies or similar technologies
				consistent with their own privacy policies. This is separate from,
				and unrelated to, any video file you process with the tool above.
			</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#2B2013]">Changes to this policy</h2>
			<p>
				If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted on this
				page.
			</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#2B2013]">Contact</h2>
			<p>
				Questions about this policy can be sent to the RapidXAI team via
				<a href="https://rapidxai.com" class="text-[#C9982E] hover:text-[#B8860B]">rapidxai.com</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
